    "We estimate that 0.58% of v14.1 contains a genuine misalignment with CPC <0.25.",
    "This is almost 6 × better than v14, suggesting that some of the improvement in v15 is due to alignment alone.",
    "At the same time, v14.1 alignment performs significantly worse around discontinuous defects (Fig. 5b), which highlights the importance of pipeline components introduced in this work.",
    "A preliminary version of our pipeline, similar to the one used for the v14.1 FAFB alignment, was applied to two mouse cortex volumes amounting to over 1.1 mm 3.",
